king.us/members/patrickw-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ePatrick\u003c/a\u003e shared this stunning portrait; one can feel the hard work for sure…\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1024x1820.jpg.webp 1024w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-169x300.jpg.webp 169w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-768x1365.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-864x1536.jpg.webp 864w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1152x2048.jpg.webp 1152w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1200x2133.jpg.webp 1200w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1980x3520.jpg.webp 1980w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-scaled.jpg.webp 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" type=\"image/webp\"/\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1820\" src=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1024x1820.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1024x1820.jpg 1024w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-169x300.jpg 169w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1152x2048.jpg 1152w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1200x2133.jpg 1200w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-1980x3520.jpg 1980w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/04-480-scaled.jpg 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ecopyright – Patrick\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eSticking with the mobile approach, he also shared this good-looking vertical panning:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-1024x2132.jpg.webp 1024w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-144x300.jpg.webp 144w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-768x1599.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-738x1536.jpg.webp 738w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-984x2048.jpg.webp 984w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-1200x2498.jpg.webp 1200w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-scaled.jpg.webp 1230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" type=\"image/webp\"/\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"2132\" src=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-1024x2132.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-1024x2132.jpg 1024w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-144x300.jpg 144w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-768x1599.jpg 768w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-738x1536.jpg 738w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-984x2048.jpg 984w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-1200x2498.jpg 1200w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/05-400-scaled.jpg 1230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ecopyright – Patrick\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFollowed by this bright shot by \u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/members/patography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ePat\u003c/a\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324-1024x768.jpg.webp 1024w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324-400x300.jpg.webp 400w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324-768x576.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324.jpg.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" type=\"image/webp\"/\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324-400x300.jpg 400w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.lightstalking.com/wp-content/uploads/06-324.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ecopyright – Pat Garrett\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eDon\u0026#39;t forget to check the photo contest winners for \u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/topic/february-2025-photo-contest-winners-visual-metaphors/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eVisual Metaphors\u003c/a\u003e; and remember, this month\u0026#39;s photo contest is now open for entries. The theme revolves on “\u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/the-essence-of-movement-april-2025/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ethe Essence of Movement\u003c/a\u003e“. Submit your photos for a chance to win $250 and please don\u0026#39;t forget voting as well. Last but not least, keep an eye out for the \u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/forum/light-stalking-group/members-picks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eMembers Picks\u003c/a\u003e — the instructions are pretty straightforward:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eMembers reference what you might consider a five star photo. Give a call out to the photographer and share their photo even if it lies in the Shark Tank and feel free to give a Critique on why it trips your Trigger. Be sure to mention the photographer and the Thread you saw it in.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAnd if you want to make out the most of your LightStalking user account, make sure to check the latest \u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eposts\u003c/a\u003e. Also, don\u0026#39;t forget to swim the \u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/topic/mobile-monday-challenge-4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eMobile Monday Challenge\u003c/a\u003e! Last but not least, Check out the current \u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/topic/what-you-reading-throwdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ereading throwdown\u003c/a\u003e, it has some nice insights and recommendations!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe\u0026#39;d Love To Hear Your Thoughts\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOur \u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/forum/the-shark-tank/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eFeedback Forum\u003c/a\u003e is a fine place for all those people wanting to grow fast as photographers. Here, you\u0026#39;ll get your work reviewed by well-intended photographers, but you\u0026#39;ll also have the chance of commenting on the work of others. We believe in the power of feedback, and here are the latest shots shared in the pool:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/topic/reflections-on-the-sunken-pond/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReflections on the Sunken Pond\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/topic/framing-the-pond/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFraming the pond\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://lightstalking.us/forums/topic/young-lady-at-mortlock-wing/\" target=\"